	   <tr><td colspan=2>12-16<br>I agree with kith on this one&nbsp;&nbsp;trissa is a great mob to solo.  She drops about .5pp inchange  and a item worth 1pp EVERY time.  You can either stay here till 17 (gets a bit slow) or leave at 16 cause there is another great place to go!<br><br>16-20<br>First and formost let me beg you ...  PLEASE PLEASE PLEASE DO NOT GO TO THE CROCS! You get jack squat for loot and you get killed by spectre trains and SG's while medding.   There is a much better place to go   its called lake rathe.  Here you will fight Aviak Guards and you might have to group with a partner till 17 but when you do hit 17 you can hunt there till 20 REAL quick. There is 2 separated spawns near the zone to the arena. If you get in trouble just zone (your abjure prolly aint high enough to cast FD comfortably). These guys dont resist much and range from lv 16-20   and they drop 1-2pp each. Some times they also drop bronze weps wich sell for 2-3pp  and also words for research!  There is a vendor across the lake and your lv 20 pet spell is 2 zones away in Ogguk ( cant buy it anywhere else).  The only draw back is change...  you will have to drop silver.  And the best part is the next place to hunt is right next door in SK.<br><br>20-30<br>Ready to get rich... good because now you will be fighting treants.  You can find them in the upper right corner of South Karana.  There usually is a group there camping both but i never had to wait for more than 30min to get in the group (necros and wizzies are the preffered class up there). The rummors of waiting 3hrs to hunt there prolly came from a melee char because no one wants them there   they die way to quick for melees to be any use.  Any way you should not have a problem hunting there   just politely ask the leader if you can join.  The treants range from like 24-29  i think.  And they drop up to 5pp in gold mostly  so you will have to beg for a banker (one time i had 1000gp and 1700sp on me)   they also drop a staff worth at least 14pp to the centaur merchants who are a 30 sec run away. They also drop words ,  pages and runes for research!  This place is rediculously safe a full grp of 20's can take one out in 10 seconds.  And the spells they cast will either be on your pets or the wizzies.  DONT USE DOTS just shadow compact to heal others and siphon life  and your pet.  You can stay here till you are through your first hell lv.<br><br>Well that is where i stand at the moment these spots are great for exp and loot   the best in my opinion.<br><br>Zastik Soulstalker<br>bristlebain server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
