	   <a name=96661024521478></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f96661024521478><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=14&mid=96661024521478>Level 29 to 33 Hunting</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=14&mid=96661024521478#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Aug 18th 10:50 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.67]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Take the boat from Freeport and hop off (literally, unless you are invisible, because the Sister at the dock will whack you.) the boat and swim to shore at the first boat stop, which is Sister Island.<br><br>For level 29 to 33 (all npcs except the merchants con GREEN at 34) you can hunt four different sisters and three dwarves.<br><br>ALWAYS pull with Dooming Darkness, as these npcs move fast even with Dooming on. Then send in pet and lifetap and DOT until they die.<br><br>NEVER FEAR!! The sisters will bring back more sisters than you can solo.<br><br>Sisters: One at end of dock (never cast on her is she is in water, as water negates all castings), one under the tree at the end of the dock, and two in a building between the dock and the solo dwarf. The two in the building require a fair amount of planning to split, so they aren't really worth your time.<br><br>Dwarves: Solo dwarf stands next to a fire on the rear of the island. In a tent beside him is a dwarf merchant. Never attack the dwarf merchant.<br><br>At the other end of the island are two dwarves, a fair amount of space apart. Find out where they are located and make sure that when you pull one, it is not in the line of sight of the second one. Otherwise you will have one dwarf too many on your hands.<br><br>Keep your pet buffed, and take your time. This is an excellent safe way to reach level 34.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
